    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1938-02-10T07:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1938-02-10T07:00:00-05:00" n="247"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d247">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">352.115 Eastern States Petroleum Co./79:
                    Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Malaga</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Callanan</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Malaga</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-02-10T12:00:00+00:00"
                            >February 10, 1938—noon</date>.<lb/>[Received 2:28 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>11. Your No. 3, February 8, 7 p.m.<note n="28" xml:id="d247fn28">Not
                        printed.</note> Captain Lewis arrived here this morning and has resumed
                    charge of the <hi rend="italic">Nantucket Chief</hi>. Port captain in reply to
                    my inquiry stated at 11:30 that his instructions were to hand over the ship to
                    Captain Lewis through the intermediary of the Consulate which he will not be
                    able to do until 4:30 p.m. today, although I requested that the matter be
                        [expedited?].<note n="29" xml:id="d247fn29">By telegram of February 10, 6
                        p.m., the Consul at Gibraltar informed the Department that the <hi
                            rend="italic">Nantucket Chief</hi> had sailed for Gibraltar at 6 p.m.
                        (352.115 Eastern States Petroleum Co./80).</note> Ambassador not
                    informed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Callanan</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
